column12: New User for Clearing Firm "671" and Exchange "CBOE" !

Tips Adapter Elimination Test Plan_W_MAI: Test Case 1:Set Underlying Recap Last Sale and verify that recap is published for the derivative product
Test Case 2:Set Underlying Recap Quote and verify that recap is published for the derivative product
Test Case 3:Underlying State change OPEN or Halted is received before Class state is in Pre-Open or Opening Rotation state. Verify that derivative class state is not changed
Test Case 4:Set the derivative class to Pre-Open state and verify that incoming underlying product state with OPEN indicator changes the derivate product to OPEN ROTATION state on the first request
Test Scenario A:Incoming Underlying Recap Last Sale only with Product State OPEN. Verify that derivative product state is changed to Opening Rotation
Test Scenario B:Incoming Underlying Recap Quote only with Product State OPEN. Verify that derivatice product state does not change

Test Case 5:Set the derivative class to Opening Rotation state and verify that incoming underlying product state with HALTED indicator changes the derivaite product to HALTED state on the first request
Test Scenario A:Incoming Underlying Recap Last Sale only with Product State HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changed to Halted
Test Scenario B:Incoming Underlying Recap Quote only with Product State HALTED. Verify that derivatice product state changed to Halted

Test Case 6:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with CLOSED state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION

Test Case 7:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with PRE-OPEN state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION

Test Case 8:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with OPENING ROTATION state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION

Test Case 9:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with OPEN state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION

Test Case 10:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with FAST state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION

Test Case 11:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with HALTED state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION

Test Case 12:Derivative class is in Pre-Open state. Incoming Underlying Recap Quote with SUSPENDED state and Recap Last Sale with various product states other than CLOSED or HALTED. Verify that derivative product state changes to OPENING ROTATION
Test Case 13:Set the derivative class to Suspended state and verify that any incoming underlying product state does not change the derivaite product state
Test Case 14:Set the derivative class to Closed state and verify that any incoming underlying product state does not change the derivaite product state
Test Case 15:Set the derivative class to Halted state and verify that any incoming underlying product state does not change the derivaite product state
Test Case 16:Set the derivative class to Open Rotation state and verify that any incoming underlying product state does not change the derivate product state except for Halted
Test Case 17:Set the derivative class to Open state and verify that any incoming underlying product state does not change the derivaite product state except for Halted
Test Case 18:Set the derivative class to Fast state and verify that any incoming underlying product state does not change the derivaite product state except for Halted

Test Case 19:Derivative option class is Halted and strategy is On-Hold state. verify that incoming underlying product state expect for CLOSED changes the derivative product state for strategy to Opening Rotation or Halted
